<section class="sec" style="background:var(--w)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-hd reveal">
      <span class="tag">What You Get</span>
      <h2 class="hdg">Everything Included in <span class="b">VIP Training</span></h2>
      <div class="div div-c"></div>
      <p class="sub">The most comprehensive dog training experience available. Jas's personal commitment to your dog's transformation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2col reveal" style="gap:16px">
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#9889;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">5 Private 2-Hour Sessions</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Five intensive one-on-one sessions with Jas Leverette personally &mdash; 10 total hours of elite training.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#127891;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Lifetime Online Course Access</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Full access to Cali K9&reg;'s complete online training library. Watch, rewatch, and reinforce forever.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128101;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">1 Year of Group Classes</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Weekly group sessions to reinforce skills in real-world environments alongside other trained dogs.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#127968;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Board &amp; Train Option</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Optional residential training where your dog lives and trains with Jas for accelerated results.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128203;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Custom Training Plan</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">A personalized blueprint built specifically for your dog's breed, age, temperament, and your goals.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#127758;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Real-World Environments</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Training happens where life happens &mdash; parks, streets, stores, and busy public environments.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128218;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Handler Education</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">You become a trained handler too. The knowledge transfers to every dog you'll ever own.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inc-item">
        <div class="inc-item-icon">&#128200;</div>
        <div>
          <div class="inc-item-title">Progress Tracking</div>
          <div class="inc-item-desc">Detailed notes and video review after each session so you can see exactly how far your dog has come.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "VIP What's Included",
  "presets": [{ "name": "VIP What's Included" }]
}
{% endschema %}
